            <div class="card-subtitle text-muted mb-3">
                <p class="card-text">The default directory structure of Rhapsody is nice and compact, with sensible naming conventions, 
                helping you to find what you need quickly. Take a moment to get familiar with where everything is located, and be sure 
                to view the notes below to avoid any conflicts as your application grows.
                </p>
            </div>
